<div style="text-align: center" class="name">
<h1 style="color:green">Lt. shri brij bihari dubey</h1>
<p style="color:red">Freedom Fighter of Rohtas (Bihar)</p>
</div>
<h2 style="color:#3366cc">Indian Independence War</h2>
    <div class="thumbnail">
    <img src="http://freedomfightersofrohtas.weebly.com/uploads/3/0/3/8/30382545/6910697_orig.jpg">
      <div class="caption-text-center">Lt. Shri Brij Bihari Dubey,<br> Convenor, Rohtas District Freedom Fighter Vestibule (Congress)
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="main" style="color:#994d00"> The <code>contents</code> are based on a book "<strong>Bharatiya Swatantrata Sangram aur Rohtas Jila</strong> (<em>Ek Aitihasik Paridrishya</em>)" by <MARK>Lt. Brij Bihari Dubey</MARK> published in <q>August 1987</q>.</p>
